TopicTitle: Would like suggestions for under water electric propulsion blades

Articles.Content:
Has anyone made propellers for the latest dlc electric motors for submarines?

I tried but was not very sucessful

There is a problem, that the new propeller blades give no lift underwater.   Tw1 has reported it as bug 23271.

The only solution I know is to use the older aerodynamics surfaces, like elevons, instead of the new propeller blades.
